<div class="bg-green-100 border-b-2 border-green-700">
  <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl mb-2">
      <%= image_tag "airport_gap_logo.png", alt: "Airport Gap logo" %>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">An API to fetch and save information about your favorite airports</h1>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center mb-2">
      <div class="mb-6 md:mb-0 md:mr-6">
        <%= link_to "Generate Token", tokens_path, class: "block bg-green-600 text-lg text-white font-bold px-6 py-4 rounded-sm hover:bg-green-800" %>
      </div>

      <div>
        <%= link_to "API Documention", docs_path, class: "block bg-purple-500 text-lg text-white font-bold px-6 py-4 rounded-sm hover:bg-purple-800" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center mt-4">
      <%= link_to "Log in to your Airport Gap account", login_path, class: "underline text-green-700 hover:text-green-900" %>
    </p>
  </section>
</div>

<div>
  <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <p class="text-lg mb-6">
      Airport Gap is a <a href="https://www.restapitutorial.com/" class="link-green">RESTful API</a> to
      help you improve your API automation testing skills. It provides access to a
      database of airports, calculate distances between airports, and allows you to
      save your favorite airports.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">API functionality available for testing</h2>

    <ul class="text-lg pl-4 list-disc list-inside mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2">Access to main HTTP methods for RESTful services (GET, POST, PUT/PATCH, DELETE)</li>
      <li class="mb-2">HTTP Token Authentication</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Data persistance - Save your favorite airports in your account</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-lg">
      Thanks to <a href="https://openflights.org/data.php" class="link-green">OpenFlights.org</a> for
      providing the airport data under the <a href="http://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1.0/" class="link-green">
      Open Database License</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="bg-green-600 border-t-2 border-green-900">
  <section class="container mx-auto px-6 pt-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-sm mb-2">
      <%= image_tag "dev_tester_logo.png", alt: "Dev Tester logo" %>
    </div>

    <p class="text-white text-center">
      Airport Gap is provided by <a href="https://dev-tester.com/" class="underline">Dev Tester</a> -
      articles and tips to help you improve your test automation skills as a developer.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center text-white">
      <%= link_to "Generate Token", tokens_path, class: "underline hover:text-green-100 pb-2 md:pb-0 px-4" %>
      <%= link_to "API Documentation", docs_path, class: "underline hover:text-green-100 pb-2 md:pb-0 px-4" %>
      <%= link_to "View Airports", airports_path, class: "underline hover:text-green-100 pb-2 md:pb-0 px-4" %>
      <%= link_to "Source Code", "https://github.com/dennmart/airport_gap", class: "underline hover:text-green-100 pb-2 md:pb-0 px-4" %>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
